data.description: Step into this lakefront property and be immediately struck by the sweeping views of the pool and lake, beautifully framed by lush palms and the fresh scent of lemongrass. Relish the stunning sunrises and peaceful evenings beside a cozy fire pit under a retractable awning.    This home has been upgraded with a new roof, efficient AC, and superior hurricane protection. It boasts a master suite with a walk-in closet and spacious shower. Additionally, there is a flexible bonus room, previously an in-law suite with its own entrance and picturesque views, ideal for rental possibilities. Benefit from low HOA fees, secure gated access, and easy access to nearby shopping and dining. Comes equipped with a new washer and dryer.
